{
  "stem": "12289.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So the other embassies were-- were left in-- in-- in the hands of younger people and so on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we had this great advantage to have a traditional embassy intact, with-- be the-- from the top till the-- to-- to-- to-- to the other staff working, where it gave us the status, at-- at least in the eyes of the-- of the Germans, and-- and-- and the status which the other embassies didn't have so much.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But here is the traditional Swedish embassy working according to-- to the national law and all that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Then, of course, they understood that we had another member of the embassy, Wallenberg, who didn't act in a very conventional way.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But we-- we let him do-- We-- we sort of closed our eyes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we let him do that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because we thought it was the only way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But it made a difference, in a way, that here is, we are working according to the old rules and all that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Raoul Wallenberg is, yes, he-- he has this special mission.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And yes, he is authorized to-- to save as many people's lives as-- as-- as possible.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So-- so that-- that made it-- that was, for me, also then very important not to go around and-- and meet and negotiate with Nazi people, here and there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I maintained the official relations with the German embassy and with the Hungarian Foreign Office.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That was my role.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It didn't prevent me from rush out and help Raoul on his-- on-- on-- when he was at the station, to help him, to liberate people and all that.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
